            INTERNET MOVIE DATABASE FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS
            ==================================================

Archive-name: movies/movie-database-faq
Last-modified: 1997/01/10
     modified: 1996/03/18

This  is  a  guide  to the Internet Movie Database (IMDB).  The database is
available   in  several  forms  on  the  Internet  and  provides  the  most
comprehensive  source  of  free on-line movie information, ranging from the
early  cinema  to  the  latest releases.  Questions about how to access the
movie database or questions which could easily be answered using it seem to
be  generating a lot of traffic these days so please keep this guide around
for reference.  Topics and questions covered are:

                           General Information
                           ===================

